Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,灰雨?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那是残云
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,准备新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那黑云没有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为孤零零的飘在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,被人们称为残云
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,猿之卷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真臭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,像臭鸡蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你能闻到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,切 一直都是我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也说几句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,和我练习说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快点说点啥吧 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是护送新娘的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,干啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,居然对喜庆的婚礼放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喜庆个屁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐是被嫁给妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嫁给妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我必须要阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一边去 我射你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,方便的话给我们说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对妖怪略知一二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那边有云
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是残云
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,以前就出现在附近吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以为了不让它吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次给妖怪准备新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它就老实回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,之后每次出现都会准备新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要是不准备的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就会被屠村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪也想要人类的新娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还要那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐说她们都被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不懂妖怪怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这次就是你姐姐被选中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我要救出姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让妖怪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这时就该我们出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥干掉过各种各样的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那云不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,当真?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不过不是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不白干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这种
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要值钱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是砂金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在河里捡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那个的话还有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要多少都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 成交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子 这是名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗也很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,才不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快承认是好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说了不要来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我来救姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为了村子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别管他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为了自己把你牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我自愿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让大家都被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让姐姐死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 那妖怪我们会收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那样就万事大吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,吃人的话肯定有嘴和肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就从那里切开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥说交给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在赶紧逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸的视线里满是火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,周围的云也是妖怪的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,被火焰之墙包围的百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次碰到什么都看不到的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是你的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐不是我的亲姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直是一个人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候爸爸和妈妈就病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有这座山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说这不再是我的山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就把我赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你受伤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是那个住在山里的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,长得像猴子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不记得自己的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只要看着姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,饥饿和寒冷就都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,过去只有妈妈才对我这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想也许…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那个姐姐是不是曾经是我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我没功夫在这哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须替姐姐报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的工作都是善始善终的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一起解决掉那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在那片云里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥不能自由行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,必须靠我们自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那片云
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是比原来更大了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是那家伙的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,蜈蚣脱皮之后会变得更大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,更大?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比现在还大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,得到新娘之后不是应该乖乖回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没准因为白天的事情生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它的弱点是日光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把它从云里拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就能打死它了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话我有一个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,干吧猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,消灭蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 姐姐的复仇战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喂这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是个大就强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的百足来我试试追
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为了姐姐的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那么大的火也烧不掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在阳光下融化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 这样也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥斩到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚才做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,被火焰之墙遮挡住视线的百鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,凭借着弓箭的声音 确定了妖怪的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 我说话的地方就是它的头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他在呼唤多罗罗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我旁边就是它的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这次总算结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,尾巴上还有一个头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你活着太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥的鼻子恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着 这是你的报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这石头是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这附近有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要不是这种石头 是砂金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那种亮晶晶的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有那些了 它们不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你们 救我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在村子里一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是一个人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了呢 猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得好好想一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,猴子就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 名字是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得你真像个姐姐一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,多罗罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个叫做气味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才好像叫我「多罗罗」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字不错吧
